name: Delia Wang's Website
body:
### Welcome to DeliaW's website!
Master of Tourism Administration graduate of the George Washington University with a concentration on Event and Meeting Management. 
Highly responsible and passionate about education with extensive experience of working with a wide spectrum of kids and adults, both domestic and international. 
An active volunteer for various kinds of conferences, meetings and special events, flexible, well-organized and detail-oriented.
Truly believe in the value of bringing people together to share, learn and grow together.
